channel.title: Strange Problem
channel.description: I am using muroth's clean deltascape client. I changed the "UserID:" to "Username:". It compiled fine. But now, when I log in as milkman, it created two accounts, one named milk and the other named man. It logged me in as man. Please help.

item.title: Strange Problem
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

try going to the section where you changed “userid:” to “username” and see if you accedentally added/changed/deleted something. if not, revert it back
